client.gui

Class CreateExamController

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.gui.CreateExamController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class CreateExamController
extends Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    CreateExamController class handle the screen of create exam by teacher. The teacher can add questions that already made and watch their details. In addition, there is option to filter questions by subject. The teacher need to choose subject, course and exam duration. Optionally, the teacher can add note to the exam.
